{"url": "https://www.cosmopolitan.com/uk/fashion/celebrity/a20270516/katy-perry-angel-wings-2018-met-gala/", "text": "Just when we thought that Rihanna had shut down the Met Gala in the most incredible Pope outfit of all time, Katy Perry stepped onto the red carpet dressed as an actual angel.\n\nThis year's theme, Heavenly Bodies: Fashion and the Catholic Imagination, has allowed celebs to really step up their game and produce some of the most creative and inventive red carpet looks the Met Ball has ever seen.\n\nNot one to shy away from a theme, Katy Perry decided to find the biggest angel wings she could and stick them on with a cute little gold mini dress.\n\nGetty Images\n\nGetty Images\n\nGetty Images\n\nGetty Images\n\nNext time we're looking for that cute accessory to go with our Saturday night outfit, we know what to do!\n\nThe singer had to travel to the Met in a vintage car with no roof - obvs those wings weren't fitting in a Toyota Prius - and then proudly took her turn on the iconic steps of the Met.\n\nWings aside, although it's really hard to ignore them, just how incredible is Katy's Versace dress?\n\nAnd those boots!\n\nGetty Images\n\nGetty Images\n\nIn case you're still hungry for more Met Gala looks, here's our roundup of all of the best outfits from the red carpet:", "images": ["https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/gettyimages-955759284-1525737137.jpg?crop=0.822xw:0.616xh;0.0914xw,0.0465xh&resize=1200:*", "https://www.cosmopolitan.com/_assets/design-tokens/fre/static/icons/search.f1c199c.svg", "https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/gettyimages-955765668-1525742036.jpg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top&resize=980:*", "https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/met-gala-awks-moments-6450dcedd49b0.jpg?crop=0.505xw:1.00xh;0.321xw,0&resize=360:*", "https://hips.hearstapps.com/rover/profile_photos/f57bc368-db57-4471-9125-3bbb3cf69392_1555067630.png?fill=1:1&resize=160:*", "https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/cara-delevingne-attends-the-frem